###

### Fetch Seller Dashboard Statistics
# Requires USER role authentication
# Returns aggregated statistics for the authenticated seller.
# @name /sales/stats [GET]
GET {{host}}/api/sales/stats?period=ALL_TIME
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Fetch Seller Dashboard Statistics - Monthly
GET {{host}}/api/sales/stats?period=MONTHLY
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "revenue": [
#     { "amount": 150.50, "currency": "ARRR" },
#     { "amount": 25.00, "currency": "YEC" }
#   ],
#   "activeOrdersCount": 3,
#   "completedOrdersCount": 12,
#   "totalAdsCount": 8,
#   "activeAdsCount": 5,
#   "period": "ALL_TIME"
# }
